11:00 am - 11:15 am: Break
11:15 am - 12:15 pm: Hands-On Lab: Write a Simple Ansible Playbook (1 hour)
12:15 pm - 1:00 pm: Lunch Break
1:00 pm - 1:30 pm: English Communication Practice (30 mins)
1:30 pm - 2:30 pm: Final Mock Interview Practice (Comprehensive) (1 hour)
2:30 pm - 3:30 pm: Review and Finalize Documentation of All Learned Concepts (1 hour)

Evening Schedule (Post-Work)
4:30 pm - 6:00 pm: Commute Home
